nail polish has gotten popular lately.

310
00:16:55,264 --> 00:16:57,474
If you want boys to think you are cute,

311
00:16:57,558 --> 00:16:59,184
you should develop
a taste for such things.

312
00:16:59,768 --> 00:17:00,644
