such tattered clothes so far.

317
00:17:10,696 --> 00:17:11,572
Of course.

318
00:17:11,655 --> 00:17:15,826
<i>Hayasaka realized that nail polish
didn't much matter with the opposite sex.</i>

319
00:17:15,909 --> 00:17:16,744
<i>However...</i>

320
00:17:16,827 --> 00:17:18,203
For boys...

321
00:17:18,871 --> 00:17:21,331
