-What is it?

324
00:17:28,005 --> 00:17:29,381
NEXT DAY

325
00:17:29,590 --> 00:17:33,302
<i>They used a kind of nail polish
that wouldn't violate the dress code.</i>

326
00:17:33,385 --> 00:17:37,890
<i>The limestone painted on the ring finger
has an appeal to modesty.</i>

327
00:17:40,184 --> 00:17:41,977
<i>What will the president think?</i>

328
00:17:42,311 --> 00:17:43,604
<i>Will he think it's cute?</i>

329
00:17:44,021 --> 00:17:48,192
<i>Or... maybe he will think
I'm being shallow?</i>

330
00:17:49,610 --> 00:17:51,987
<i>What are you intending to do?
What's with those nails?</i>

331
00:17:52,488 --> 00:17:53,864
<i>They're just nice.</i>

332
00:17:55,824 --> 00:17:59,495
<i>I would hate it if he asked me like that.</i>

333
00:18:01,747 --> 00:18:03,791
<i>I'll go home today, after all.</i>

334
00:18:03,874 --> 00:18:04,958
What are you doing, Shinomiya?

335
00:18:06,585 --> 00:18:07,628
Aren't you going in?

336
00:18:08,045 --> 00:18:10,589
No, I am going in.

337
00:18:13,842 --> 00:18:15,052
Kaguya!

338
00:18:16,053 --> 00:18:17,888
I have a question about this part.

339
00:18:18,138 --> 00:18:20,724
Yes, what is it?

340
00:18:23,060 --> 00:18:24,812
Are you hiding something behind your back?

341
00:18:25,187 --> 00:18:26,855
No, nothing at all.

342
00:18:28,524 --> 00:18:31,276
<i>She always has good intuition
in times like this.</i>

343
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:33,862
<i>If someone were to notice,
I want it to be the president.</i>

344
00:18:33,946 --> 00:18:36,156
<i>Even if it's wrong,
I don't want this kid to notice.</i>

345
00:18:36,573 --> 00:18:38,158
<i>I have to get closer to him.</i>

346
00:18:39,326 --> 00:18:43,038
